Apex Triggers

Before 
no extra DML 
same object
fire error 
update / prepopulate fields

After 
DML needed
related objects
other conditions

1 before insert 
validate data , set default values , modify fields before saving to DB , Fire error 
2 after insert 
preform actions , like creating related records , send email
3 before update 
validate data , modify data , prevent changes
4 after update
trigger follow up logic , notifications , email , log changes , sync related data
5 before delete
prevent deletion (add error) , validation
6 after delete
clean up related things ,  cascade delete , log data
7 after undelete
recreate relationship , reconnect related records

2
auto create child record (contact) for every account
List<Contact> contoCreate = new List<Contact>();
for(Account acc:Trigger.new)
{
 Contact c = new Contact();
 c.Name = acc.Name;
 c.AccountId = acc.Id;
 contoCreate.add(c); 
}
insert contoCreate;
}

3 before update
for(Account acc:Trigger.new)
 for(Account oldacc:Trigger.oldmap.get(acc.Id))
   if(acc.Name!=oldacc.Name)
     acc.addError('Account name cannot be changed');

5 before delete
5a active account cannot be deleted
for(Account oldacc:Trigger.old)
   if(oldacc.Active__c=='YES')
       oldacc.addError('Active account cannot be deleted');

5b prevent deletion if child record exits
Parent = acc, Child = contact
for(Account acc:Trigger.old)
   Integer countChild = [Select COUNT() from Contact where AccountID IN:acc.Id];
if(countChild > 0) acc.addError('Cannot delete account because it has contacts');



delete - only old , oldmap
